channel.title: How do i change my client port?
channel.description: Hi, I wanna know how to change the port for my client from 43594 to 5555 its a Bluur's Base heavily modified but i dont know how to change port[br][br][size=1]Posted on: October 10, 2009, 04:35:03 pm[/size][hr]BUMMPPPP!!!!

item.title: How do i change my client port?
item.dc:creator: @lilwermscape_ftw lilwermscape_ftw
item.description:
@lilwermscape_ftw wrote:

[quote=“GrimReapersScythe, post:3, topic:307657”][quote author=lilwermscape_ftw link=topic=403805.msg2989519#msg2989519 date=1255214702]
go to client files and open client.java…
hit ctrl + f to search.
type in 43594 and change all to 5555.

should work
[/quote]
This actually depends. Some clients load it through the gui. So he’s going to have to try both.[/quote]

true that… like he said do both
